     *  <code>setScrollBarProperties()</code> method.
     *  Allowed values are <code>ScrollPolicy.ON</code>,
     *  <code>ScrollPolicy.OFF</code>, and <code>ScrollPolicy.AUTO</code>.
     *  MXML values can be <code>"on"</code>, <code>"off"</code>,
